@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

participant "Client" as Client
participant "<&clock> Timer" as Timer
participant "Coordinator" as Coord

== Run 1 ==
Client -> Coord : start write
note over Timer : timeout boundary at T
Coord -> Coord : quorum ack arrives at T - small delta
Coord -[#green]> Client : success

== Run 2 ==
Client -> Coord : start write
note over Timer : timeout boundary at T
Coord -> Coord : quorum ack arrives at T + small delta
Timer -> Coord : timeout fires
Coord -[#red]x Client : timeout failure

note over Client, Coord
A tiny shift in timing can change which branch executes.
end note
@enduml
